                            <Data>[ Notes ]-[ Breaking Through ]

Damn! This piece of crap! If I can get this drilling machine to work again, I just might be able to dig my way through an Old Entrance to the Main Facility (which has supposedly been buried for years), and break through to my friends trapped inside the building. 

I hope Ling knew what she was talking about and that this Old Entrance through the Buried Caverns really exists; I know she has access to all of the blueprints for the facility (what with her being in charge of the Nuclear Reactor and needing to know of any possible vulnerabilities to the building’s structural integrity), but maybe the entrance is just a rumor. It doesn’t matter. I have to try.

The drilling machine should be safe in the garage while I travel to the Old Supply Depot across the Bridge and look for some spare parts to repair the vehicle with.

-Diego Martinez
Junior Engineer
R.O.S. Industries

GPS:Old Buried Entrance:-3557.56:20430.56:-30419.77:</Data>
